nodes.text: Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Coloring Book (1984)

The Star Wars: Return of the Jedi Coloring Book was published by Kenner Products in 1984. It shares the same title with two other coloring books published by Kenner in 1983, one featuring Max Rebo on the cover and another featuring Luke Skywalker. This particular coloring book features Lando Calrissian on the cover and is identified by the product number 19350.
